MAAC Community Charter School holds an annual scholarship fundraiser called Battlegroundz during which students and invited artists paint murals in an alley behind the school , the paper said . But when complaints about the mural poured in , the school covered it with black plastic and then with what appeared to be plywood late last week , the Union - Tribune said .
